%aR%?if(%mp,<=,3)<%?mv(1)<ÏÐ|%?mp<ÅÆ|ËÌ|ÅÆ>>|ÅÆ>%?if(%ft(themes/Themify_2.preferences,minimal player mode:),=,on)<|%?if(%pe,!=,1)<ÇÇ>>È
